@startuml validate_standalone
title Validate as a Standalone Gate

participant "Software Architect" as architect
participant "Core" as bausteinsicht_cli_core
participant "Loader" as bausteinsicht_model_loader
participant "Validate" as bausteinsicht_model_validate

architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_core : 1. bausteinsicht validate (CI job or pre-commit hook)
bausteinsicht_cli_core -> bausteinsicht_model_loader : 2. Load(model.jsonc)
bausteinsicht_cli_core -> bausteinsicht_model_validate : 3. Validate(schema, references, constraints)
bausteinsicht_model_validate --> bausteinsicht_cli_core : 4. ok, or field-level errors
bausteinsicht_cli_core --> architect : 5. exit 0, or exit 1 with errors (blocks the commit/pipeline)

@enduml
